      "patch": "@@ -13,6 +13,7 @@ <h1>TurboQuant <span class=\"dim\">Image Similarity</span></h1>\n       <p class=\"subtitle\">Click any image to find similar ones. The entire image index is just 0.2 MB (compressed from 1.5 MB).</p>\n       <p class=\"note\">1,000 Unsplash photos. Each image is represented by a 384-dim embedding vector, compressed 6x with TurboQuant.\n         Similarity is computed directly on the compressed vectors \u2014 no decompression needed.</p>\n+      <nav class=\"demo-nav\"><a href=\"./\">All demos</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/turboquant-wasm\">npm</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://github.com/teamchong/turboquant-wasm\">GitHub</a></nav>\n     </div>\n \n     <div id=\"main\">"
