      "patch": "@@ -13,6 +13,7 @@ <h1>TurboQuant <span class=\"dim\">Vector Search</span></h1>\n       <p class=\"subtitle\">Search 5K Wikipedia passages entirely in your browser. The search index is 1.2 MB instead of 7.7 MB.</p>\n       <p class=\"note\">Left: TurboQuant searches compressed vectors directly (no decompression). Right: brute-force on full float32 vectors.\n         Top results match. Borderline results near the cutoff may swap \u2014 that's the tradeoff for 6x less data.</p>\n+      <nav class=\"demo-nav\"><a href=\"./\">All demos</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/turboquant-wasm\">npm</a> \u00b7 <a href=\"https://github.com/teamchong/turboquant-wasm\">GitHub</a></nav>\n     </div>\n \n     <div id=\"main\">"
